quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,70,"Wọ́n wí pé: “Ǹjẹ́ àwa kò ti kọ̀ fún ọ (nípa gbígba àlejò) àwọn ẹ̀dá?”"
  15,71,"Ó sọ pé: “Àwọn ọmọbìnrin mi nìwọ̀nyí, tí ẹ bá ní n̄ǹkan tí ẹ fẹ́ (fi wọ́n) ṣe.”1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Hūd; 11:78.]
  15,72,"(Allāhu sọ pé): “Mo fi ìṣẹ̀mí ìwọ (Ànábì Muhammad) búra;dájúdájú wọ́n kúkú wà nínú ìṣìnà àti àìmọ̀kan wọn, tí wọ́n ń pa rìdàrìdà.” {1}",footnotes:1:[Ti Allāhu - subhānahu wa ta‘ālā - ni kí Ó fi ohun tí Ó bá fẹ́ búra. TiRẹ̀ sì ni kí Ó fí ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́ búra. Àmọ́ àwa ẹ̀dá Rẹ̀ kò gbọ́dọ̀ fi n̄ǹkan mìíràn lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀ búra gẹ́gẹ́ bí a kò ṣe gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún n̄ǹkan mìíràn lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀.]
  16,49,"Allāhu sì ni ohunkóhun tó wà nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ohunkóhun tó wà nínú ilẹ̀ ní n̄ǹkan abẹ̀mí àti àwọn mọlāika ń forí kanlẹ̀ fún. Wọn kò sì ṣègbéraga.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah ar-Ra‘d; 13:15.]
  16,50,"Wọ́n ń páyà Olúwa wọn tó ń bẹ lókè wọn. Wọ́n sì ń ṣe ohun tí À ń pa láṣẹ fún wọn.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ tún wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-’Ani‘ām; 6:18 àti sūrah al-Mujādilah; 58:7.]
  16,51,"Allāhu sọ pé: “Ẹ má ṣe jọ́sìn fún ọlọ́hun méjì. Òun nìkan ni Ọlọ́hun Ọ̀kan ṣoṣo tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo. Nítorí náà, Èmi (nìkan) ni kí ẹ bẹ̀rù.”"
  17,16,"Nígbà tí A bá sì gbèrò láti pa ìlú kan run, A máa pa àwọn onígbẹdẹmukẹ ìlú náà láṣẹ (rere). Àmọ́ wọ́n máa ṣèbàjẹ́ sínú ìlú. Ọ̀rọ̀ náà yó sì kò lé wọn lórí. A ó sì pa wọ́n rẹ́ pátápátá.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Āyah yìí jọ sūrah al-’Ani‘ām; 6:123.]
  17,17,"Mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ìran tí A ti parun lẹ́yìn (Ànábì) Nūh! Olúwa rẹ tó ní Alámọ̀tán, Olùríran nípa àwọn ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀."
  17,18,"Ẹni tí ó bá ń gbèrò (oore) ayé yìí (nìkan), A máa taari ohun tí A bá fẹ́ sí i nínú rẹ̀ ní kíákíá fún ẹni tí A bá fẹ́. Lẹ́yìn náà, A máa ṣe iná Jahanamọ fún un; ó máa wọ inú rẹ̀ ní ẹni yẹpẹrẹ, ẹni ẹ̀kọ̀."